data.title: "Verbotene Liebe" Episode #1.3703 (TV Episode 2010)
data.meta_description: Episode #1.3703: Directed by Claude Giffel. With Wolfram Grandezka, Jens Hartwig, Jana Sch√∂lermann, Miriam Lahnstein. Andi and Helena's announcement they're off to Cambodia for a year means for Tristan he'll probably be dependent on tacky substitute Jessica that long. Feeling guilty about her adulterous dreams makes Nathalie avoid Constantine except for Spanish lessons. Ansgar tells the police it was self-defense against an unknown blackmailer with pictures of him and a prostitute. Once the cops realize he must have known Jens from his trial for kidnapping Sebastian he's arrested as murder-suspect, a scandal the shaken form can hardly afford.
